Privacy Policy for Turpo ERP

At Turbo ERP, we are committed to protecting the privacy of our users. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose personal information through our ERP application.

Information We Collect

We collect information from users when they register for our ERP application, use our services, or communicate with us through our website or support channels. The information we collect may include:

Contact information, such as name, email address, and phone number
Company information, such as name and address
Payment information, such as credit card numbers and billing addresses
Usage data, such as login information and device information
Communication data, such as email and chat messages

How We Use Information

We use the information we collect for the following purposes:

To provide and improve our ERP application services
To communicate with users about their accounts, orders, and services
To send promotional communications and updates about our services
To respond to user inquiries and support requests

How We Share Information

We may share information with third parties in the following circumstances:

To provide and improve our ERP application services
To comply with legal obligations or court orders
To protect and defend our rights and interests
To transfer assets in connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets

Security

We take appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of personal information. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee the absolute security of personal information.

User Rights

Users have the right to access, correct, and delete their personal information. They can also object to the processing of their personal information and withdraw their consent at any time. To exercise these rights, users can contact us using the contact information provided in this privacy policy.

Changes to Privacy Policy

We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify users of any changes by posting the updated policy on our website and updating the "Last Updated" date.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or our privacy practices, please contact us using the contact information provided in this privacy policy.

This privacy policy is effective as of 23/04/2023.
